Version 0.3.0-alpha ----------------------------------------------- [2015-03-03]

*   Added description tag to metadata.

*   Changed publishing information to reflect the publication of the book rather
    than the original paper (as it's supposed to be according to the EPUB spec).

*   Books's subject list now uses BISAC categories.

*   Styling no longer uses absolute positioning (which apparently causes
    problems with some readers).


Version 0.0.2-alpha ----------------------------------------------- [2015-02-24]

*   Simplified markup and styling.
*   Changed chapter naming scheme from "chapter-0N" to "chapter-N".


Version 0.0.1-alpha ----------------------------------------------- [2013-08-04]

*   "Utilitarianism" by John Stuart Mill EPUB ebook first release.
